{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f001",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 250,
      "y": -120,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 80,
      "color": "6",
      "text": "# 🦞 OpenClaw × LinkedIn Auto-Posting Flow\nComplete lifecycle: Daily Briefing → Publish → Review → Optimize"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f100",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 0,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 350,
      "label": "Phase 1: Daily Briefing & Content Production (Mon/Wed/Fri)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f101",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## 📰 Daily AI Briefing\n\nPushed at 8:30 AM (Beijing)\nSources: PYMNTS / TechCrunch /\nKrebs on Security / Brave Search\nTopics: AI in Finance / Anti-fraud"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f102",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 310,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## 🎯 Topic Selection\n\nPick from today's briefing\nFocus: AI Finance / Anti-fraud /\nCompliance / RegTech\nCheck perspective rotation log"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f103",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## ✍️ AI Auto-Drafting\n\nAlternate CEO ↔ PM perspective\nHook → Context → Insight →\nStory → Takeaway → CTA\n800-1300 chars, short punchy lines"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f104",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 930,
      "y": 40,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "5",
      "text": "## 🎨 Cover Image Gen\n\nHTML Canvas / OpenAI\nCanva-style 1024×1024\nPlaywright screenshot\n→ PNG"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f105",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Cron trigger:** UTC 0:30\n**Only pushed once** by cron\nNever duplicate in chat session"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f106",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 310,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Perspective log:**\nLast: PM (2026-03-10)\nNext: CEO\nStored in HEARTBEAT.md"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f107",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Skills used:**\nlinkedin-content\nlinkedin-authority-builder\naccountant / financial-literacy"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f108",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 930,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Storage:**\nlinkedin-drafts/\ndraft-YYYY-MM-DD-{topic}.md\n+ images/"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f200",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 400,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 200,
      "label": "Phase 2: Human Review (Feishu)",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f201",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## 📱 Feishu Preview Push\n\nPost text + cover image sent together\nOwner reviews content & image\nCan request revisions anytime"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f202",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 430,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## ✅ Owner Approval\n\nOwner says \"Go\" / \"OK\" / \"Approved\"\n→ Triggers publish flow\n⚠️ NEVER skip review!\n⚠️ NEVER publish text-only (must have image)!"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f203",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 810,
      "y": 440,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "3",
      "text": "## 🔄 Revision Loop\n\nOwner requests changes →\nRevise draft / regenerate image →\nRe-send preview →\nWait for approval again"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f300",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 650,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 320,
      "label": "Phase 3: Publish & Post-Publish Engagement",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f301",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 🚀 LinkedIn API Publish\n\n1. Register image upload → asset\n2. Upload PNG to LinkedIn\n3. Publish with IMAGE type\n4. Record Post ID"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f302",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 310,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 💬 First Comment\n\nWithin 30 min of publishing:\nDrop company website link\nin the first comment\n(No external links in post body!)"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f303",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 270,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 🔁 Reply to Comments\n\nWithin 1 hour of publishing:\nReply to ALL comments\nFirst-hour engagement is critical\nfor algorithm boost"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f304",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 930,
      "y": 690,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 130,
      "color": "4",
      "text": "## 📁 Archive\n\nMove draft to\npublished/ folder\nRecord Post ID\nUpdate perspective log"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f305",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 850,
      "width": 560,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Skill:** linkedin-poster (⚠️ needs LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID + SECRET config)\n**API:** OAuth 2.0 + ugcPosts v2 | IMAGE type for image posts"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f306",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 850,
      "width": 510,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Algorithm signals:** Comments > Shares > Likes\nFirst hour decides reach | Question endings boost engagement\nPersonal stories + insights = highest interaction type"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f400",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 1020,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 200,
      "label": "Phase 4: Industry Engagement (After Each Post)",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f401",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 🔍 Search Trending Posts\n\nSearch AI in Finance / AI Anti-fraud\nFind 3-5 high-quality posts\nTarget: CFO, FinTech founders,\nCompliance leaders, AI in Finance KOLs"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f402",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## ✏️ Draft Comments\n\nWrite 3-5 thoughtful comment drafts\nAdd value, not just \"great post!\"\nShow expertise in our domain\nSend drafts to owner via Feishu"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f403",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 800,
      "y": 1060,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "## 👤 Owner Posts Manually\n\nOwner reviews & posts comments\nNever auto-comment (ban risk!)\nGoal: build visibility in\nAI + Finance community"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f500",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 1270,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 220,
      "label": "Phase 5: Weekly Performance Review (Sunday)",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f501",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1310,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 📊 Data Collection\n\nSunday 8PM Beijing: remind owner\nOwner screenshots LinkedIn\nanalytics dashboard\nSend screenshots to Feishu"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f502",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 1310,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 🔬 AI Analysis\n\nCompare impressions / engagement /\ncomments across all posts\nIdentify best-performing post\nAnalyze what worked & why"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f503",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 640,
      "y": 1310,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 📋 Strategy Optimization\n\nOutput: performance report\n+ next week content strategy\nAdjust topics / tone / format\nFeed insights back to Phase 1"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f504",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 960,
      "y": 1310,
      "width": 170,
      "height": 140,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "## 🔮 Future\n\nPlan B: LinkedIn\nAPI auto-pull\n(needs r_member_\nsocial scope)\nCurrently: manual\nscreenshot"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f600",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 1540,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 180,
      "label": "Tech Stack & Config",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f601",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1580,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**OpenClaw** → Feishu Bot (WebSocket)\n**LinkedIn API** → OAuth 2.0 + ugcPosts v2\n**Image Gen** → HTML/CSS + Playwright / OpenAI\n**News** → Brave Search API + RSS feeds"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f602",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420,
      "y": 1580,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Schedule:** Mon/Wed/Fri posting\n**Publish window:** Tue/Thu 8-9 AM AEST\n**Heartbeat cron** → auto-trigger\n**Briefing:** Daily 8:30 AM Beijing (UTC 0:30)"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f603",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 840,
      "y": 1580,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**Hashtag strategy:**\n1-2 broad (#AI #FinTech #Leadership)\n+ 2-3 niche (#FraudDetection\n#AICompliance #CFO #RegTech)\n3-5 per post, at the end"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f700",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -50,
      "y": 1770,
      "width": 1200,
      "height": 140,
      "label": "Future Upgrade Path",
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f701",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 1810,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "🎬 **Video content** if text ROI plateaus\n2-3 min max | Script by AI | Subtitles mandatory\n(80% watch on mute) | Skill: video-subtitles"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f702",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420,
      "y": 1810,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "📈 **Auto analytics** via LinkedIn API\nNeeds Community Management API approval\nr_member_social scope → auto-pull metrics\nEliminate manual screenshot step"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0a1b2c3d4e5f703",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 840,
      "y": 1810,
      "width": 290,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "🤖 **linkedin-poster skill**\nStatus: ⚠️ pending config\nNeeds: LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID\n+ LINKEDIN_CLIENT_SECRET"
    }
  ],
